name: Rumah Intaran
address: V5WG+HXC, Bengkala, Kubutambahan, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81171, Indonesia
review 1:
Inspirational vernacular architecture NOW WITH YUMMY RESTAURANT SERVING MEALS.
I explored the wood fire kitchens grounds and workshop spaces and then popped by at the Warung Bebek Pesona for a yummy meal of fried duck with rice, tofu, tempe, cucumber and kemangi basil. The sambal and fried galangal garnish sure hit the spot!
review 2: A learning place about northern Bali culture and culinary.

name: Pengalaman Rasa Gastronomy
address: Rumah Intaran, Jl. Gn. Batur, Bengkala, Kec. Kubutambahan, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81172, Indonesia
review 1: We had a wonderful experience! The chef was so kind and made such beautiful food. Truely from farm to table. I learnt about different local ingredients that I’ve never seen before. Thank you so much!
review 2: Such an amazing place to discover the real taste of Bali ❤️ I definitely recommend it for those who are looking to live a unique experience in this island.
